              <div class="svc-meta">
                <span class="pill">Downtime: Minimal</span>
                <span class="pill">Relief: Weeks–months</span>
              </div>
              <span class="svc-link">Learn more →</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/services/juvederm-fillers" class="svc-card group">
              <div class="svc-head">
                <h3 class="svc-title">Dermal Fillers</h3>
                <p class="svc-sub">JUVÉDERM® Collection</p>
              </div>
              <p class="svc-desc">Structure & balance with restraint for harmony.</p>
              <div class="svc-meta">
                <span class="pill">Results: Immediate</span>
                <span class="pill">Refine: 2–4 weeks</span>
              </div>
              <span class="svc-link">Learn more →</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/services/prp-microneedling" class="svc-card group">
              <div class="svc-head">
                <h3 class="svc-title">PRP Microneedling</h3>
                <p class="svc-sub">Texture • Pores • Scars</p>
              </div>
              <p class="svc-desc">Collagen induction using your platelet-rich plasma.</p>
              <div class="svc-meta">
                <span class="pill">Series recommended</span>
