              <span class="svc-link">Explore →</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/services/microneedling" class="svc-card group">
              <div class="svc-head">
                <h3 class="svc-title">Microneedling (SkinPen®)</h3>
                <p class="svc-sub">C.I.T. • Proven device</p>
              </div>
              <p class="svc-desc">Collagen induction for texture, pores & scars.</p>
              <div class="svc-meta"><span class="pill">Series recommended</span><span class="pill">Gradual results</span></div>
              <span class="svc-link">Learn more →</span>
            </a>

            <a href="/services" class="svc-card group">
              <div class="svc-head">
                <h3 class="svc-title">Acne Programs</h3>
                <p class="svc-sub">Face Reality Boot Camp</p>
              </div>
              <p class="svc-desc">Guided protocols to clear & maintain skin.</p>
              <div class="svc-meta"><span class="pill">Clinical coaching</span><span class="pill">Home care plan</span></div>
